Package: podium-cli
Version: 1.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io, git, curl
Maintainer: Cane Bay Computers <info@canecomputers.com>
Description: Universal PHP Development Environment
 Podium is a comprehensive Docker-based development platform that creates
 professional PHP development environments with complete automation.
 .
 Manage multiple projects across different frameworks - Laravel, WordPress,
 and generic PHP - all running simultaneously with shared services.
 .
 Features:
  * One-command project creation
  * Cross-framework compatibility (Laravel, WordPress, PHP)
  * Shared services (MySQL, Redis, phpMyAdmin)
  * LAN access for team collaboration
  * Containerized development tools
  * Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS)
Homepage: https://github.com/CaneBayComputers/podium-cli
